### Create a new book
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Great Gatsby",
  "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
  "genre": "Fiction",
  "description": "A novel set in the Jazz Age."
}

###

### Get all books
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books

###

### Get a book by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/{{bookId}}

###

### Update a book by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Great Gatsby",
  "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
  "genre": "Classics",
  "description": "A novel set in the Roaring Twenties."
}

###

### Delete a book by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/books/{{bookId}}

###

### Create a new review
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "{{bookId}}",
  "userId": "1a2b3c4d5e",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "An excellent read!"
}

###

### Get all reviews
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews

###

### Get a review by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/{{reviewId}}

###

### Update a review by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/{{reviewId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "A good read, but could be better."
}

###

### Delete a review by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/{{reviewId}}
